values: OMG.. im going fucking crazy here. i need ppl. i need friends. n now i see who my true friends are.. out of all my riends on here i get one gosh damn comment ... it was short but at least she tryed to help n stuff.. i was right. no one hardly does care.. why am i here????????????

I havent wrote in here in a long ass time.. ur probabably wondering how im doing for the ones who havent talked to me in like for ever.. Well... Im fucking pissed. upset, depressed, crushed, lonely, hurt, sad, angry. n i can keep going too.. For a while i was starting to not show any feelings to anyone id keep them all hidin inside me cus i was afraid to be hurt by anyone.. well about 3 months ago i let them go.. for this one special person. the one i loved with all my heart. Not this puppy shit love with.. marriage love..for once i was happy.. everything in my life was ok when i could be with him. then he took off to college in NY. so we didnt see each other much. we were on the phone everyday for hours n when the phones were free no joke we probably talked for  like 6 hrs...he said he couldnt do this long distance anymore it was hurting him n he needed someone there. He was coming here in 2 weeks bk to visit me, but i guess he couldnt wait....n i had planed out a surprise for him. before i went to college next may i was flying there to visit him n hopefully get accepcted to the college in NY. that way we could be together n get a place then.. But its too late now. He called last night n left me a voicemail while i was in church.. he said we had two things to talk about. n they werent so good.. my heart just droped right then n there. n the tears i couldnt hold bk but i had to cus i couldnt do that in front of anyone at church. I called him bk n yeah long story short. he broke it up. for some chick named megan... she has a myspace.  if u want to look at it tell me n ill send u a link.. PLZZZ do look n tell me whats wrong with the picture. why he left me for her.. she is nothing but a fat ugly immature lil girl who is a  peice of worthless shit who deserves nothing! anyways.i know ull all say ull get over it. its ok... dude u dont understand we were closer then b/f g/f...we were lets say engaged but no one knew...now its over i lost what i had going for me.. life isnt worth it anymore it seems.. it hurts so bad... it hurts worse now then it did when a family member died who was close to me. Thats messed up! my heart has been shot, n blown up n the pain is overwhelming.. it will never go away, i cant do this.n he says he still wants to be friends. n talk everyday n come out here n see me.. OMG do u know how much more that hurts right there.. thats like a tease or something. i dont get it... i let everything go in my life my feelings my emotions, my actions towards others. n i got it slamed right bk at me... why did i do it.. i dont think i can ever do that again. im going bk behind my wall which has grown even bigger now.. all my friends think im happy n al but its only a mask that is put on to hide the tears, the frown, the pain n the lonelyness that im am in.... plz someone comment n help me!
